{"tid":1883180,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本新增6宗武漢肺炎個案 60多歲男醫生中招","createTime":"2020-02-16T18:20:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T08:43:55.000Z","uid":60545,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6cd4eac167b113a0f8aa57d45ab11f971e41ebf8","tid":1883180,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T18:20:12.000Z","msg":"日本共同社報導，東京都政府16日宣布新增5名武漢肺炎確診病例，包括一名60多歲男醫師。這名男醫師和先前確診的一名女護士在同家醫院工作，這名護士曾和13日確診的70多歲計程車司機參加同場春酒宴。<br />\n<br />\n其他4例確診病例中，有兩人和確診計程車司機參加同場春酒。另外2例分別是住在東京的30多歲男性及住在東京附近的60多歲男性。<br />\n<br />\n而愛知縣亦再多1宗確診個案，令全日本累計個案增至59宗。新增患者是住在尾張地方的60多歲男性，是去美國夏威夷旅行的名古屋夫婦中女方的朋友，15日發燒38度求診，16日接受測試，確診入院。（By Wikipedia )<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/120944/4348966\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F120944%2F4348966&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQwZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=522926dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/120944/4348966</a>"},{"pid":"0f3ba6644dba221cfea8297cda071a918eb6d7df","tid":1883180,"uid":129169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T18:21:20.000Z","msg":"4代<br />\n大陸人&gt;的士佬&gt;護士&gt;醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"085d33ad30088dbd9fb03ae299a80e53ab07bade","tid":1883180,"uid":265179,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T18:22:12.000Z","msg":"等睇日本爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d2df2d00eb3f67a205b09950308c6401164d61","tid":1883180,"uid":92188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"085d33ad30088dbd9fb03ae299a80e53ab07bade","tid":1883180,"uid":265179,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T18:22:12.000Z","msg":"等睇日本爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T18:32:21.000Z","msg":"都幾肯定會爆<br />\n仲要而家個政府乜都唔做<br />\n學埋支那啲衰嘢，想大事化小，驚佢連奧運都出事"},{"pid":"fb3b4ffb0e498607e2a6f48a7a92c36b6f